      "id": "low_spec_parallelism_gate",
      "standard": "成本异常检测的进程池并行必须默认关闭，只能通过 COST_MONITOR_ENABLE_PROCESS_POOL 显式开启。",
      "evidence": [
        "anomaly_engine._should_use_parallel_detection",
        "COST_MONITOR_ENABLE_PROCESS_POOL"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "regression_with_db_restore",
      "standard": "运营回归脚本必须在执行后恢复本地数据库族文件，避免测试数据污染正式预览库。",
      "evidence": [
        "scripts.run_ops_regression.snapshot_db_family",
        "scripts.run_ops_regression.restore_db_family"
      ]
